    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "If we implement REPL mode I guess users will expect to get values of PowerShell variables ​​from PowerShell and return modified ones. I do not know if it is possible to do this conveniently, but the types of _inlining_ have always been met in many languages ​​before.\r\nI'm sure if PowerShell is a powerful add-on over .Net we should consider C# script mode too.",
